            Recruit at UIC Business
          Heading link



 
Copy link






Build a presence on campus with a hybrid recruiting formula.
Virtual Information Sessions
Connect with students about potential internship and job opportunities. We will help you market the event to qualified candidates.
On-Campus and Virtual Career Fairs
Target and engage internship and full-time candidates at a Business Career Fair. From registration to the end of the fair, we are here at every step.
On-Campus and Virtual Interviews
Select your optimal date and interview method, and we will facilitate an interview schedule to kick off your hiring process. Recruiting Coordinators provide support with student outreach and scheduling interviews.
To reserve a date, email Tracy Warner at warner@uic.edu
Branding Days
Reserve space in the lobby of Douglass Hall for employer tabling. Meet and greet students in between classes to promote your organization and opportunities. Table stand displays and giveaways are encouraged.











